            <!-- <img src="animals.jpg" style="width: 150px; height: 120px;"> -->
            <div class="modal-body">a) Insect pests:<br>
            Stem bores and grasshoppers are serious pests of bajra controlled by two sprayings with 2 litres of Eldrin 20 c.c and
            grasshoppers may be controlled by dusting the crop with BHC 5 percent.<br><br>
            
            b) Diseases:<br>
            Downy mildew- for controlling this disease seed treatment with fungicide like Dithane Z-78 or M-45 @ 2.0kg/ha in
