            Smut- Treatment with Ceresan or Thirum @ 1-2 g/kg seeds is effective.<br>
            Ergot- Seed treatment with 20% common salt solution followed by washing with fresh water and then treating with Ceresan
            or Thirum @ 1-2 g/kg seeds is effective</div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
